課程大綱










藥物治療專題討論（一）CASE CONFERENCE OF PHARMACOTHERAPY






開課系所 Department/Institute:  臨藥科技        Institute of Clinical Pharmacy and Pharmaceutical Sciences
開課教師 Instructor:   高雅慧 Yang-Kao, Yea-Huei            ;王明誠 Wang, Ming-Cheng              
開課學年 Academic Year:   0102
開課學期 Semester:    2
開課序號 Serial Number:   009

課程屬性碼 Attribute Code:   CP  6007 
課程碼 Course Number:   S650610 
分班碼 Class Code: 
學分數 No. of Credits:           1
